HEADWORD: Reprimer
<hw>Re*prim"er</hw> <pr>(r?-pr?m"?r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Firearms)</fld> <def>A machine or implement for applying fresh
primers to spent cartridge shells, so that the shells be used
again.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

